bzh.plealog.bioinfo.ui.blast.config

Class ConfigManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • bzh.plealog.bioinfo.ui.blast.config.ConfigManager

  • public class ConfigManager
extends Object
    This class is the configuration manager of BLASTViewer. It stores a list of available configuration using a Map where the key is the name of a configuration and the corresponding value is an AbstractConfig object.
    Author:
    Patrick G. Durand
